      "content": "For a truly sophisticated, globally recognized look, aim for classic, tailored silhouettes that transcend fleeting trends. Think impeccably fitted, high-quality suiting in neutral tones like charcoal, navy, or camel, paired with crisp, high-thread-count shirts. Accessories should be understated but expensive—a fine watch or silk tie—to signal quality without needing loud displays. This timeless, minimalist approach speaks to inherent class rather than regional fashion fads.",
